    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome to Robo Hunt: Dive into an exhilarating multiplayer experience where three players join forces to battle a formidable boss monster, controlled by a fourth player. This is not your ordinary boss fight—strategize, adapt, and conquer in a dynamic environment where every map brings new twists and mechanics.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Key Features:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Asymmetric Multiplayer Combat:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Engage in thrilling 3v1 battles where teamwork and strategy are paramount. Three hunters with unique abilities face off against a powerful player-controlled boss monster.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008310/extras/15aec213f1b5f4f1f49fa35d3bd2a585.poster.avif?t=1738823614\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008310/extras/15aec213f1b5f4f1f49fa35d3bd2a585.webm?t=1738823614\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008310/extras/15aec213f1b5f4f1f49fa35d3bd2a585.mp4?t=1738823614\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Diverse Hunter Classes:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choose from a variety of hunter classes, each with distinct abilities and playstyles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008310/extras/32a252357b31cc77b5ed862436976289.avif?t=1738823614\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008310/extras_big/32a252357b31cc77b5ed862436976289.avif?t=1738823614 width=800 height=428 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Formidable Boss Monsters:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Take on the role of the boss monster and unleash chaos with devastating attacks and unique powers. Each monster offers a different challenge, requiring hunters to adapt their strategies.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008310/extras/9228ee862d30e859afd4f08a9bb97cef.poster.avif?t=1738823614\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008310/extras/9228ee862d30e859afd4f08a9bb97cef.webm?t=1738823614\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008310/extras/9228ee862d30e859afd4f08a9bb97cef.mp4?t=1738823614\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Dynamic Maps with Unique Mechanics:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore diverse maps, each featuring its own set of twists and mechanics that can turn the tide of battle.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008310/extras/b1a114e6d36b9a47bf375228f826821a.poster.avif?t=1738823614\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008310/extras/b1a114e6d36b9a47bf375228f826821a.webm?t=1738823614\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008310/extras/b1a114e6d36b9a47bf375228f826821a.mp4?t=1738823614\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Strategic Depth:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Coordinate with your team to develop strategies that exploit the boss's weaknesses. Communication and adaptation are key to victory.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008310/extras/b52337323ea7a7a073d5fffb9a05974f.poster.avif?t=1738823614\" width=480 height=270 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008310/extras/b52337323ea7a7a073d5fffb9a05974f.webm?t=1738823614\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3008310/extras/b52337323ea7a7a073d5fffb9a05974f.mp4?t=1738823614\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
